          <p>Repository Finder, a pilot project of the <a href="http://www.copdess.org/enabling-fair-data-project/">Enabling FAIR Data Project</a> led by the American Geophysical Union (AGU) 
            in partnership with DataCite and the Earth, space and environment sciences community, can help you find an appropriate repository to deposit your research data.
            The tool is hosted by DataCite and queries the re3data registry of research data repositories.</p>

            <p>As part of the <a href="https://www.fairsfair.eu/">FAIRsFAIR project</a>, which aims to supply practical solutions for the use of the 
            FAIR data principles throughout the research data life cycle, the Repository Finder is extended to query for repositories relavent to FAIRsFAIR Project.</p>

